  "title": "🌟Early Career🌟 Sales Executive 🌸",
  "description": "<p>Experience level: Entry Level / Early Career </p><p>💖 ABOUT THE ROLE</p><p>Are you confident and love communicating with people? 🗣️💬</p><p><br />We’re looking for a motivated and good looking Sales & Marketing Executive to help us grow our clients’s brand, build exciting new campaigns, and connect with customers in fresh, sincere authentic ways 📈<br /><br /><br />If you enjoy team-work and learning real world business skills — this role is for you 🚀</p><p><br />✨ What You’ll Be Doing</p><p><br />🎯 Promote products and services through in person campaigns</p><p>💬 Talk to customers, understand their needs, and build relationships </p><p>📊 Track campaigns results and share ideas to improve performance</p><p>🤝 Work with a supportive, energetic team on fun projects</p><p>🧠 Learn sales, branding, communication, and confidence building skills </p><p><br />🌈 Who We’re Looking For</p><p><br />💡Positive, can-do mindset</p><p>🌍 Team player who loves learning and growing </p><p>🥳 No formal experience required — just enthusiasm and willingness to learn 🙌🏻</p><p><br />👉🏻 Ready to start your journey? Apply now and let’s grow together 🌸🚀</p>",
